    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "adnought",
      "PAN AMERICAN WORLD AIRWAYS\nLATIN AMERICAN DIVISION - BOLIVAR, 21 — MEXICQ, D. F.\nOFFICE OF\nF. S. ADAMS\nDecember 16, 1946\nOpt. Sharron\nPAA Sr. Pilot\nMunicipal Airport\nBrownsvilk, Texas\nDear Captain:\nI am sending you herewith a set\nof the\npictures taken at the inauguration of the; :\nnew international wing to the Mexico City\nairport. Neither Mr. Rojas nor his staff\nhave been able to locate any of the pic-\ntures of the DO-4 to which you referred\nin your last conversation. Mr. Rojas is\nunder the impression that those pictures\nmust not have been taken by his department.\nIf you can give me any more informa-\nt1on,\nI shall be glad to try and run them\ndown for you.\nWarm personal regards.\nT. S. Adams.\nencs.",
      "COMPANIA MEXICANA DE•AVIACION\nMEXICO, D. F.\nADMINISTRADOR DE CORREOS: NO ES CORREO DE PRIMERA CLASE PUEDE ABRIRSE PARA SU REVISION\nCPI. SHARRON, PAA SR. PILOT\nMUNICIPAL AIRPORT\nBROWNSVILLE, TEXAS\nAIRCO\nFORMA T-52 (8-46) 10-M\nUNITING ALL MEXICO\nUNIENDO A TODO MEXICO"
    ],
